text: MetroPlus zĩi-sa yaa soãma wʋsgo la a ka giin ni neb ye, la a ligda waoga biilfo, ni ri fãa a ligda keten ka ta tẽng-pug tẽra meng ligd yerope puge ye.

Fo sã n ka minmi n zote mobil tẽng so-baaneg zugu, bi f nadg-pang ni f yam: zĩi-gondgma toe-toea, soya seoklma, la so-golong sileng n waoge.

Gasgã zug zĩige ra yaa sɛk-zĩigẽ n pa wõnd a taaba kõ wẽnnaamã.
Babilon nebã mee b wẽnnaamsã fãaa wẽnd-doo kasẽngã sẽn n da mi wa wẽnnaamã saka.
Wend-root kuda wʋsg fãa wakate ning tara paka daara gagdien sibra yʋngo paka da-yopoend-baasga gilli, ne paam taab n min lebg n tʋg n yi tigr yʋng-suk wakate n na yilli deem a kiris vʋʋgre.
Wẽnd-doog fãaa da tara roog n pak la sɛk-zĩigẽ maan-kʋʋda rãmb bal n tõe kẽ.
Tẽedba baooda pẽem wʋsgo, n paam bãngre sẽn n kẽede ne Wẽnnaam sɩdem sɩdema/ Wẽnnaam bɩ Wẽnnaam dãmba.
Nowɛlle yaa vʋʋsem wakate kasenga ni kiris neba, ub le maanda a tigra wã Zezi dogem daare.
Tẽnga yaa wẽnd-tuudm ziiga se n ya nɛ wẽnd-tuudma soyã n yeti wẽnd yaa yembrã - Judaisma, kiristẽebã la silaamdã, n le ya ziig n yaa tagsgo, tẽebo,la rogõmik ziiga.
boka mẽng, sẽn n tõog n ket n be baa ne a sẽn kaosã, kõta kaset hakiik ne Muhamad siiga ratm.
Haldarsvík tẽn-kõaka kota gesgo n taagd Eysturoy ko-gub-tẽnga sene laa tar babga-nĩi wend-doogo n ka wenda taab ye.
